text: Burhan Bozkurt (born 1934) is a Turkish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman flyweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Turkey Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
